HTSeq
#GO SEA
goSEA_HTseq <- enrichGO(
  gene = rownames(sigRes_HTSeq),
  OrgDb = org.Mm.eg.db,
  keyType = "SYMBOL",
  ont = "BP", #BP, MF or CC
  pAdjustMethod = "BH",
  pvalueCutoff = 0.05,
  qvalueCutoff = 0.05)

## [3] "GeneRatio"                      "BgRatio"

## [7] "qvalue"                         "Negative_log10_adjusted_PValue"

ggplot(df, 
       aes(x = Negative_log10_adjusted_PValue, 
           y = reorder(Pathway_Description, 
                       Negative_log10_adjusted_PValue), 
           label=ID)) +
  
  geom_bar(stat = "identity")+

    size=4,
    min.segment.length = 10,
    hjust = 0.5, 
    vjust = 0.5)+
